author: @Navarrosriffs
text: Because I'm sure people are going to say something about Tae not wearing satin, I'll explain. Taehyung has a skin condition called cholinergic urticaria. Cholinergic urticariaÂ (also calledÂ cholinergicÂ angioedema or heat bumps) is a reaction that results in tiny hives surrounded by large patches of red skin. They're related to an increase in your body temperature. You can get itchy red hives on your skin for lots of reasons. If he were to have worn the satin, he definitely would've have got a reaction from it because satin is a very heat absorbant fabric. He wore this outfit to make sure he didn't get Itchy Itchy and could enjoy performing! Thank you!
